. Hit record and you are done. Share your video on all social media platforms!\nViso is under development with the ever-growing collection of Avatars, Rooms, and Props.", "short_description": "Record yourself, in the avatar of your choice in VR.\n\nVISO discord\uff1ahttps://discord.gg/PXN2knydJ9\nViso is a video recording application in VR. Wanna capture your dance moves? Well, now you can. Choose your own avatar, scene setting, and music. Hit record and you are done. Share your video on all social media platforms!\nViso is under development with the ever-growing collection of Avatars, Rooms, and Props."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.roarwildstudio.com/viso/PrivacyPolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.roarwildstudio.com/viso/TermsOfService.html", "publisher_name": "Roar Wild Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.roarwildstudio.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "393222478507326"}, {"id": "1228796255027646"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ART_CREATIVITY", "PRODUCTIVITY", "MUSIC_VIDEO"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "1241190206669705"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PENDING", "id": "601450018399719"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "5896302520470022"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "5896302520470022"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1667420160, "status": "PENDING", "id"